"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?15/32/15881?source=related_link\">",
"      Limb-girdle muscular dystrophy",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?40/0/40968?source=related_link\">",
"      Overview of paraneoplastic syndromes of the nervous system",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?26/22/26983?source=related_link\">",
"      Paraneoplastic cerebellar degeneration",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?41/35/42552?source=related_link\">",
